snippet.title: Debra Katz (Debra Lynne Katz)
snippet.description: Debra Lynne Katz is founder of The International School of Clairvoyance. She is a filmmaker and also author of 3 books: "You Are Psychic", Extraordinary Psychic" and "Freeing The Genie Within".
